Gas price is 0 if the the contract runs on ANVIL chain;
immutable and constant variables are part of contracts bytecode;
Reading and writing from "Storage" is expensive
In a contract, all the solidity functions are coverted into function selector
Use error statements instead of just using require statement to meet a particular condition
Also make sure that the error should be named with the name of of contract , in order to know which contract has reverted thef error